Martial Training V										SORTKEY:Martial Training 5	CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:Combat		PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Martial Training IV												PREMULT:1,[PREATT:11],[PRESKILL:1,Knowledge (Martial)=11]																																																																																										DESC:You may select two new maneuvers or one new maneuver and one new stance from your chosen discipline of up to 5th level, and you may ready an additional maneuver. You may also trade out any one maneuver from your chosen discipline you know and replace it with a different maneuver from that discipline of up to 4th level. You must meet the minimum initiator level to select any maneuver.																																																																																																																																																																																																																						BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Martial Training Choice|1																																													BONUS:VAR|MartialTrainingManeuversReadied|1	BONUS:VAR|MartialTrainingFeatManeuverLevel|1																																	SOURCEPAGE:p.24
