Powerful Mark																CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:Combat		PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=Special Ability,Warder ~ Armiger's Mark																																																																																																												DESC:The penalty for your armiger's mark ability increases by 2, and the save DC for your armiger's mark grand challenge increases by +2.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																					BONUS:VAR|WarderArmigersMarkPenalty|2	BONUS:VAR|WarderImprovedArmigersMarkDC|2																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.24
Ricochet Weapon																CATEGORY:FEAT		TYPE:Combat		PREABILITY:1,CATEGORY=FEAT,Point-Blank Shot																																																																			PRESTAT:1,DEX=13																																										DESC:Whenever you throw a weapon as part of a martial strike, that weapon bounces or ricochets off your target and returns to your hand at the end of your turn. You must have a free hand to be able to catch the weapon on its return, otherwise it falls into your space at your feet.																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																																													SOURCEPAGE:p.24
